-- Ford set to rename Five Hundred sedan "Taurus": DJ
-- 
-- Tue Feb 6, 2007 6:07am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/06/us-ford-taurus-idUSN0618550420070206

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Ford Motor Co. ( F.N ) is planning to announce that its Five Hundred mid-size sedan will be renamed the Taurus, after its once-popular but now discontinued model, Dow Jones Newswires reported on Tuesday. 


 The newswire said Ford executives would announce its plan on Wednesday at the Chicago auto show. No Ford spokesman was immediately available to comment.